### POST /api/v1/trips
### Descripción: Crear viaje. Requiere JWT + X-Tenant-Id + Idempotency-Key.
### Headers requeridos: Authorization: Bearer <token>, X-Tenant-Id: <guid>, Idempotency-Key: <string>
### Códigos: 200 OK (TripDto) | 400 IDEMPOTENCY_KEY_REQUIRED, etc.

# @name createTrip
POST {{BASE_URL}}/api/v1/trips
Authorization: Bearer {{ACCESS_TOKEN}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{TENANT_ID}}
Idempotency-Key: trip-{{$guid}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pickupLatitude": 19.4326,
  "pickupLongitude": -99.1332,
  "dropoffLatitude": 19.4350,
  "dropoffLongitude": -99.1400,
  "pickupAddress": "Origen",
  "dropoffAddress": "Destino",
  "estimatedAmount": 12.50,
  "currency": "USD"
}

### Response esperado (200):
# {
#   "id", "status", "pickupAddress", "dropoffAddress", "estimatedAmount", "finalAmount", "currency", "createdAtUtc"
# }

### Response error (400): IDEMPOTENCY_KEY_REQUIRED, TENANT_REQUIRED, etc.
